# Stage 8: Battle Victory Ending

label stage8_ending_battle_victory:
    scene bg garden with fade

    show m at center with dissolve

    m "The Echo is contained. New wards. New bindings."

    "But this time, the binding is different."
    "Not cruel. Not ignorant."
    "A compromise forced through necessity."

    show s at left with dissolve

    s "It's stable. But I fear we've only delayed the inevitable."

    "The Echo remains. Conscious. Contained."
    "Not at peace. But not rampaging either."

    "Sometimes you wonder if you made the right choice."
    "Power over compassion. Safety over freedom."

    "The academy is safe. But at what cost?"

    $ ending_type = "pyrrhic_victory"

    jump stage8_epilogue_solo
